<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      background-color: #e7f0ea !important;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .textColor {
      color: #052311;
    }

    .primaryColor {
      color: #0e6431;
    }

    .headline {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .titleSize {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .textSize {
      font-size: 0.975rem;
    }

    .btnStyle {
      background-color: #0e6431;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 15px 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      height: 54px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      font-size: 1.375rem;
    }

    .importantText {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0e6431;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1 class="headline" style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    Your Credential for Shuttle bus
  </h1>
  <h1 class="titleSize">
    Hi,
    <span class="primaryColor" style="font-weight: 700">
      <%=name%>
    </span>
  </h1>
  <p class="textSize" style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    We are writing to inform you that your credentials have been sent to your
    gmail account. Please find the login details below:
  </p>
  <p class="textSize">
    Username: <span class="importantText">
      <%=email%>
    </span>
  </p>
  <p class="textSize">
    Password: <span class="importantText">
      <%=password%>
    </span>
  </p>

  <p class="textSize" style="padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px">
    We recommend that you change your password after logging in for the first
    time to ensure the security of your account.
  </p>

  <p class="textSize">Best regrads</p>
  <p class="textSize">Shuttle bus team</p>
  <p class="textSize">
    If you still have some problem please contact us on :
    <span class="importantText">lorssyleang20@kit.edu.kh</span>
  </p>
</body>

</html>